<h2 id="for-prospective-students">For Prospective students</h2>

<p>We are affiliated with the <a href="https://plantbio.okstate.edu/graduate-programs">Plant Biology M.S. program, and the interdisciplinary Plant Sciences Ph.D. program</a> offered by the Department of Plant Biology, Ecology and Evolution at the Oklahoma State University. For application deadlines/instructions, see the <a href="https://plantbio.okstate.edu/graduate-programs/prospective-students">department web site</a>.</p>

<h2 id="about-the-lab">About the Lab</h2>

<p>Our group is located at 321 Physical Sciences, <a href="https://plantbio.okstate.edu/">Department of Plant Biology, Ecology and Evolution</a> at the Oklahoma State University in Stillwater, Oklahoma.</p>

